channel.title: Teleport command help
channel.description:
I have a PI based server. It won't do some commands that I see on tutorials, even the simplest, IE: Teleporting.
I need someone to connect to my teamviewer, and teach me how to make a simple command, because this server seems like it's not compatible with very much. I know someone is going to copy and paste some code in here, and then I try it, and I just get compiling errors. So anyways, someone please help =)
